'From Small-Land 3.8-5976-0266 of 2 September 2004 [latest update: #5976] on 7 September 2004 at 6:36:54 pm'!"Change Set:		PreferenceBalloonHelpDelayTime-dgdDate:			7 September 2004Author:			Diego Gomez DeckNew preference to remove the hardcoded value in Morph>>balloonHelpDelayTime.The default for the new preference is, as usual, the previous hardcoded value."!!Morph methodsFor: 'halos and balloon help' stamp: 'dgd 9/7/2004 18:35'!balloonHelpDelayTime	"Return the number of milliseconds before a balloon help should be put up on the receiver. The balloon help will only be put up if the receiver responds to #wantsBalloon by returning true."	^ Preferences balloonHelpDelayTime! !!Preferences class methodsFor: 'misc' stamp: 'dgd 9/7/2004 18:35'!balloonHelpDelayTime	"Answer the number of milliseconds before a balloon help 	should be put up on morphs."	^ Parameters		at: #balloonHelpDelayTime		ifAbsent: [800]! !